<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Daneric</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-15 03:16:43</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am a wiz that has 202 intelligence, so yes, I agree with the comments above about it being a decent robe to wear even if I am level 45.  If ya ask me though, I think the Oracle Robe is rather ugly itself. I like the stats boost on the Drape better than the Oracle anyway. Being an Erudite, I also look better in green :) I won't upgrade my robe until I get a nice one from the planes. And no, I am not wasting dough or items on an SMR either. On my server (Rathe) SMRs are starting to become commonplace too. I'll stick with my newbie-looking Green Drape robe and will always keep it as a spare even if I ever get a planes item. The save poison is worth it in certain situations. <BR>
