<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Thorwald</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-04 20:47:09</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I obtained this item from the Noxious spider in Sol B as we were camping the bugs. I would not recommend the place for anything less than a full group of level 40's. Unless you want to gamble seriously. Also, the spider is likely to be quickly pulled and killed by *someone*, not because of the drape, but because of the rare drop, the Golden Chitin Bracelet.<BR>
<BR>
The spider is pretty hard, has a decent poison DoT, and hits pretty fast and hard, over 100 in double attacks. Around where it spawns is a variety of bugs, all extremely dangerous except for a 40 group. Those as as much trouble as the Nox spider itself. Do look out for the Stone spider! It will slaughter even a 40 group unless you are careful. Pretty immune to magic, and hits for 120+. Is about level 45.<BR>
<BR>
Stay safe, and be warned ;-)<BR>
<BR>
Thorwald Steelarm, Leader of the Order of Mjolnir, Tunare.</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
