If only it weren't so incredibly ugly.  However, the dex will make my (soon to be acquired) incandescent wand proc much more frequently, I hope.  Pity I acquired it after I trivialed out in cured silk - the poison resist would have helped out a lot with those crags.</font></td></tr></table>
