<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Apparently these are somewhat common at higher levels.<BR>
<BR>
I'm only a level 7 enchanter.  I was leveling in East Freeport... and I sold someone my damask robe.. I paid 20PP for this, because it "looked cool!"  They paid me 50PP! and they said, "Hey you need a robe?"  I was about to buy a Sr. Apprentice Robe... then he handed me a Green Silken Drape.  Anyway, it looks very cool with illusion half elf.  Makes you look like Robin Hood, stats aren't bad either  :) :) :)   It looks just like a high elf newbie robe, but what the hey?<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
